## Icons & motion

- **Icons — STRICT:** dùng **`@phosphor-icons/react`** cho TẤT CẢ icon; import đúng icon dùng (tree-shaking friendly). **CẤM `lucide-react`** (và mọi icon lib khác). Có usage lucide còn sót → thay bằng Phosphor tương đương (vd `Volume2`→`SpeakerHigh`, `VolumeOff`→`SpeakerSlash`, `Settings`→`GearSix`, `Maximize`→`ArrowsOut`, `Flame`→`Fire`, `Radio`→`Broadcast`, `ArrowLeft`→`ArrowLeft`). Icon map (`Record<Enum, Icon>`) để ở `map.tsx`, type icon dùng `Icon` của Phosphor (`@phosphor-icons/react`), KHÔNG `LucideProps`.
- **Motion:** `framer-motion` only where animation is required; avoid wrapping large static regions.

---

## Data fetching (SWR)

- Configure SWR via **`src/components/providers/SwrProvider.tsx`** (or the project’s single provider). Do not duplicate global SWR config in every hook.
- Custom hooks that wrap `useSWR` live next to the feature or under a `hooks/` folder if the project introduces one—**one hook per file** for non-trivial logic.

---

## Comments — STRICT (mirror backend)

- **ENGLISH ONLY — no Vietnamese in code.** Every comment, JSDoc, inline note, `TODO`/`FIXME`, and identifier (variable/function/type/file name) MUST be in English. The product is going international; reviewers and contributors may not read Vietnamese. This applies to ALL `.ts`/`.tsx` under `src/`. (User-facing copy stays in i18n message files `src/messages/*.json` — never hardcode Vietnamese strings in components; do not "translate" the `vi.json` content.)
- **JSDoc cho TẤT CẢ:** mọi component, hook, util, function (kể cả nội bộ không export nếu logic không hiển nhiên), type, interface, field, enum + member, constant, map, config object, GraphQL op. KHÔNG còn "chỉ khi non-obvious".
- **Hook / util / op:** JSDoc kèm `@param` (mô tả từng param) + `@returns`.
- **Component:** JSDoc trên export mô tả vai trò + lý do `"use client"`/a11y nếu có.
- **Handler phức tạp:** comment `//` giữa các bước lớn (validate → call API → update UI state).
- **Enum/constant:** comment trên enum + từng member/giá trị (đơn vị, ý nghĩa).

---

## Accessibility & semantics

- Prefer **semantic HTML** (`main`, `nav`, `article`, headings in order).
- Interactive elements must be **keyboard reachable**; use HeroUI/native controls instead of `div` with `onClick` unless there is a clear a11y pattern.

---

## ESLint

1. Read **`eslint.config.mjs`** (or project ESLint config) before large style changes.
2. Run **`npm run lint`** and fix issues so changes pass the project’s rules.

Code must pass ESLint in addition to the conventions above.
